long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Falling Dots is a fun skill game where we try to collect the red dots and pay attention to the black dots falling from above.
As usual, you challenge multi-colored dots. We collect the red dots by paying attention to the black dots in this area. By collecting the red dots, we can progress and get points. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Falling Dots has emerged as a fun skill game designed for us children's game lovers.
You can play this game for free. You can play with your mouse or the keyboard. You can play this game on touch screens by tapping or swiping your mobile phone or tablet.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Falling Dots Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
